<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.2.6">
<l>neyvā yaḻalam puturan tumunnīr tuṇiyap paṇikoṇ ṭaṇiyārn tilaṅku</l>
<l>maiyār  maṇivaṇ ṇaṉaiyeṇ ṇinuntam maṉattē yiruttum paṭivā ḻavallīr</l>
<l>avvā yiḷamaṅ kaiyarppē cavuntā ṉarumā maṟaiyan taṇarcin taipuka</l>
<l>cevvāyk kiḷināṉ maṟaipā ṭutillait tiruccit rakūṭam ceṉṟucēr miṉkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who are able to live so that, thinking of the one</l>
<l rend="indent">whose hue is of a rare dark jewel, who sparkles full of gems,</l>
<l>Having taken [on] the task to split the three-watered [ocean],</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] shooting an oil-tipped arrow of fire, [you] fix [him] in your minds,</l>
<l>Go and gather at Tiruccitrakūṭam in Tillai where red-beaked parakeets</l>
<l rend="indent">sing the four Vedas,</l>
<l>Even though little girls’ lips pronounced [them] so the thoughts of priests</l>
<l rend="indent">of the great, rare Vedas are captivated.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
